  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Versatile and Efficient",
      "text": "Discover enhanced network efficiency with the MikroTik CRS106-1C-5S. Designed to elevate connectivity, this intelligent desktop smart switch offers a compact solution that effectively blends versatility with high-performance capabilities. Equipped with one Gigabit Ethernet / SFP combo port and five 1.25Gbps SFP cages, the CRS106-1C-5S offers a flexible range of connectivity options. This configuration enables different devices and applications to easily join your network, ensuring smooth data flow and effective traffic control."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Built For Practicality",
      "text": "With a 400MHz CPU and 128MB of RAM, the CRS106-1C-5S is designed to manage data-intensive tasks with ease. The smart switch runs RouterOS with an L5 license, providing a robust foundation for advanced networking capabilities. Its capability to support 11-30V power adds to its adaptability across different power sources. The CRS106-1C-5S features a practical design, housed in a compact desktop case. An external AC/DC adapter is included for a convenient and dependable power supply."
    }
  ],
